            "answer_text": "When you sum up a lot of errors there are two key factors: Is the mean 0?Are they independent?If both are true, then, while it is possible to get a huge error, it is very unlikely. But be careful! It is easy to assume that both are true when they are not. This accounts for a lot of major screwups. ",
